data.description: Welcome to your dream country estate! This stunning property offers almost 8 acres of gorgeous land and a spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home that is sure to impress. 8 acres of land to explore and enjoy. The fenced fields are perfect for horses or other livestock, and the large concrete building is ideal for storing equipment or hosting gatherings. Whether you are looking for a peaceful retreat or a place to entertain family and friends, this property offers it all. Don't miss your opportunity to own this incredible piece of country paradise.
